videoSnippet.title: Artificial Inteligence Leela Zero to Become as Strong as Alpha Zero? | Only if We Help!
videoSnippet.description:
#agadmator Hello Everyone! Meet Leela Chess Zero
This project is called Leela Chess Zero (http://lczero.org/). 
Great progress has been made so far - Leela has gone from random play to around 1800 now on average hardware in four weeks. 
The catch is that project relies on people running Leela on their computers so there are more matches for Leela to learn from.

Play against Leela here  http://play.lczero.org/
Leela on Reddit https://www.reddit.com/r/chess/comments/882jr8/leela_chess_zero_the_fork_of_leela_zero_for_chess/
Download Leela here https://github.com/glinscott/leela-chess/wiki/Getting-Started
